descript.abstract: Spreadsheet from Bob Hidekamp in County Engineers. Placed by DOTE in the City of Cincinnati via coordinate information from Survey data.Not all HCE monuments are shown - only old "City Bench Marks" and the 60 GPS points from original start up of CAGIS.Ths layer contains primarily the Monument name and/or number; X;Y;Z - X&Y are the 1983 Datum; Z is the 1929 Datum
descript.purpose: Shows Bench Marks - mainly used by Surveyors - normally provides the State Plane Coordinate (X,Y) and Elevation (Z)
